First Lady Melania Trump recently met with leaders from top companies and associations to discuss the impact of the internet and technology on children. The meeting focused on various topics such as teaching empathy and kindness offline, promoting social and emotional wellness in children, ensuring safe online behavior, and improving online safety through effective solutions and public policies. Representatives from each platform shared lessons they have learned and discussed the challenges they currently face. Melania Trump emphasized the importance of open communication with children about the potential dangers of technology and the opportunity to teach positive online behaviors. She expressed gratitude to the technology experts for their collaboration and highlighted the need to educate children about the power of positivity.